(secondQuint)Zika Case Definition and Surveillance Study.

 This prospective, multicenter, cohort study will conduct active and passive surveillance for ZVD and determine its prevalence and seroconversion incidence in areas of Latin America experiencing Zika epidemic activity.

 A description of the occurrence of dengue virus and chikungunya virus infections in the cohort may also be provided as differential diagnosis of ZVD.

